<div id="content" class="backgrnd4"><div id="right"><div id="box6"><h2 class="backgrnd12"><span class="text1">Proceedings of the Seventeenth Innovative Applications of Artificial IntelligenceConference</span></h2><div class="content"><p><i>Sponsored by the Association for the Advancement of Artificial Intelligence</i></p><p><b>Edited by Neil Jacobstein and Bruce Porter</b></p><p>July 9 &ndash; 13 2005, Pittsburgh, Pennsylvania. Published by The AAAI Press, Menlo Park, California. <a href="../../Press/Proceedings/aaai05.php">This proceedings is also available in book and CD format.</a></p><p><b>Please Note:</b> Abstracts are linked to individual titles, and will appear in a separate browser window. Full-text versions of the papers are linked to the abstract text. Access to full text may be restricted to AAAI members. PDF file sizes may be large!</p><hr /><h3 class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2005/iaai05-000.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Contents</a></h3><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2005/iaai05-019.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Preface</a> / vii<br /><i>Neil Jacobstein and Bruce Porter</i></p><h4 class="left">Deployed Application Papers</h4><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2005/iaai05-001.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Automating the Underwriting of Insurance Applications</a> / 1451<br /><i>Kareem S. Aggour and William Cheetham</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2005/iaai05-002.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Loads&ndash;n-Limits and Release-n-Sequence: The &ldquo;Brains&rdquo; behind WEPS</a> / 1459<br /><i>Paul S. Cerkez</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2005/iaai05-003.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Scheduling Engineering Works for the MTR Corporation in Hong Kong</a> / 1467<br /><i>Andy Hon Wai Chun, Dennis Wai Ming Yeung, Garbbie Pui Shan Lam, Daniel Lai, Richard Keefe, Jerome Lam, and Helena Chan</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2005/iaai05-004.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Knowledge-based Interactive Selling of Financial Services with FSAdvisor</a> / 1475<br /><i>Alexander Felfernig and Alfred Kiener</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2005/iaai05-005.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">TEXTAL&trade;: Automated Crystallographic Protein Structure Determination</a> / 1483<br /><i>Kreshna Gopal, Tod Romo, Erik McKee, Kevin Childs, Lalji Kanbi, Reetal Pai, Jacob Smith, James Sacchettini, and Thomas Ioerger</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2005/iaai05-006.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">NESTA: NASA Engineering Shuttle Telemetry Agent</a> / 1491<br /><i>Glenn S. Semmel, Steven R. Davis, Kurt W. Leucht, Dan A. Rowe, Kevin E. Smith, and Ladislau B&ouml;l&ouml;ni</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2005/iaai05-007.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">CORMS AI: Decision Support System for Monitoring US Maritime Environment</a> / 1499<br /><i>Haleh Vafaie and Carl Cecere</i></p><h3 class="left">Emerging Applications</h3><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2005/iaai05-008.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Boosting Sex Identification Performance</a> / 1508<br /><i>Shumeet Baluja and Henry Rowley</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2005/iaai05-009.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">The Deep Space Network Scheduling Problem</a> / 1514<br /><i>Bradley J. Clement and Mark D. Johnston</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2005/iaai05-010.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">A Multi-Agent Simulator for Teaching Police Allocation</a> / 1521<br /><i>Vasco Furtado and Eurico Vasconcelos</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2005/iaai05-011.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Markov Decision Processes for Control of a Sensor Network-based Health Monitoring System</a> / 1529<br /><i>Anand Panangadan, Syed Muhammad Ali, and Ashit Talukder</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2005/iaai05-012.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Automatically Acquiring Domain Knowledge For Adaptive Game AI Using Evolutionary Learning</a> / 1535<br /><i>Marc J. V. Ponsen, H&eacute;ctor Mu&ntilde;oz-Avila, Pieter Spronck, and David W. Aha</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2005/iaai05-013.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Activity Recognition from Accelerometer Data</a> / 1541<br /><i>Nishkam Ravi, Nikhil Dandekar, Preetham Mysore, and Michael L. Littman</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2005/iaai05-014.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Development of a Hybrid Knowledge-Based System for Multiobjective Optimization of Power Distribution System Operations</a> / 1547<br /><i>Robert J. S&aacute;rfi and A. M. G. Solo</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2005/iaai05-015.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">The DEFACTO System: Training Tool for Incident Commanders</a> / 1555<br /><i>Nathan Schurr, Janusz Marecki, J. P. Lewis, Milind Tambe, and Paul Scerri</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2005/iaai05-016.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">A Knowledge-Based Approach to Network Security: Applying Cyc in the Domain of Network Risk Assessment</a> / 1563<br /><i>Blake Shepard, Cynthia Matuszek, C. Bruce Fraser, William Wechtenhiser, David Crabbe, Zelal G&uuml;ng&ouml;rd&uuml;, John Jantos, Todd Hughes, Larry Lefkowitz, Michael Witbrock, Doug Lenat, and Erik Larson</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2005/iaai05-017.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Managing the Life Cycle of Plans</a> / 1569<br /><i>Biplav Srivastava, Jussi Vanhatalo, and Jana Koehler</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2005/iaai05-018.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">A Learning Architecture for Automating the Intelligent Environment</a> / 1576<br /><i>G. Michael Youngblood, Diane J. Cook, and Lawrence B. Holder</i></p></div></div></div><div id="left">
